460b16631a3a9be30f67c0ee7062f0f3","tid":2058207,"uid":87799,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:05:44.000Z","msg":"利申 聽返黎<br />\n成日搞唔掂d野要OT<br />\n為左唔比老闆知佢咁廢<br />\n6點打左卡先再OT<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3534b836bb62656daeeb22aed5302a1dc428449","tid":2058207,"uid":157098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"成班同事收咗工去食飯<br />\n有個食食下無啦啦話要去剪頭髮<br />\n來來回回出咗去幾次返黎 個頭都冇唔同到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d293f25b1981286e3640b530d37327c077845108","tid":2058207,"uid":252492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:57:30.000Z","msg":"2020年4月2日更新：<br />\n原來施sir同黑社會關係咁密切<br />\n齊齊撈改裝街車生意重借埋架車比黑社會去禁錮虐打勒索人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n李梓峰 IG狂罵LIHKG<br />\n但比人起底係施小聰FB揾食群組其他ADMIN<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同以前係施sir任教學校學生</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2vXap9m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2vXap9m.png&h=ec92bcf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BAoQp9q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBAoQp9q.png&h=1f385436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d68MHV9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd68MHV9.png&h=0390adea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pfqGwPw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpfqGwPw.png&h=ec948ce9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n15歲少年南生圍遭禁錮虐打拍裸照 3人被控勒索等6罪<br />\n<br />\n均報稱無業的曹樂謙（17歲）、張曜龍（18歲）及汽車技術員<span style=\"color: red;\">李梓峰</span>（21歲）同被控於今年3月28日在元朗南生圍路南生圍近燈柱AD0561的路邊襲擊、非法禁錮、以恫嚇方式要求少年X交出港幣40000元，並偷竊屬於X的一部手提電話及一張香港身分證，共值1500元。<span style=\"color: red;\">李梓峰</span>另被控於同日同地無牌駕駛私家車<span style=\"color: red;\">UX3994</span>，並運載超過該車輛登記文件的5名乘客。<br />\n<br />\n警方28日接報，30、31日拘捕5男2女，年齡介乎14至30歲，包括14歲學生、無業、銷售員、汽車維修員，部分人有<span style=\"color: red;\">黑社會背景</span>，全部人持有香港身份證，涉嫌非法禁錮、盜竊、勒索、襲擊導致身體傷害，全部被扣留調查，案件繼續調查中，不排除更多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cB7xDu8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcB7xDu8.png&h=5a533761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2x9FJy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2x9FJy.png&h=ef64381f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nnfy7oD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnfy7oD.png&h=b03676e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1738254/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-15%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D%E9%81%AD%E7%A6%81%E9%8C%AE%E8%99%90%E6%89%93%E6%8B%8D%E8%A3%B8%E7%85%A7-3%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%8B%92%E7%B4%A2%E7%AD%896%E7%BD%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1738254%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-15%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%258D%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%258C%25AE%25E8%2599%2590%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%258B%258D%25E8%25A3%25B8%25E7%2585%25A7-3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%258B%2592%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E7%25AD%25896%25E7%25BD%25AA&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa5Aoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=e6a7cdbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1738254%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-15%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%258D%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%258C%25AE%25E8%2599%2590%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%258B%258D%25E8%25A3%25B8%25E7%2585%25A7-3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%258B%2592%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E7%25AD%25896%25E7%25BD%25AA&h=a41f6563\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1738254/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-15%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D%E9%81%AD%E7%A6%81%E9%8C%AE%E8%99%90%E6%89%93%E6%8B%8D%E8%A3%B8%E7%85%A7-3%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%8B%92%E7%B4%A2%E7%AD%896%E7%BD%AA</a>"},{"pid":"88f5ec03e7c1c8277d80e08a95c7f524072ca1f3","tid":2058207,"uid":252492,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:57:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以下內容轉自原樓主會員苦主<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">追擊教畜大王</span></ins>前兩個POST</span><br />\n<br />\n(多圖/汽車)屯門某中學老師不問自取及爭人錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1140844\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1140844</a><br />\n施小聰&amp;池凱欣 不問自取及拖欠退款（二）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1142885\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1142885</a><br />\n青衣小學老師 施小聰&amp;池凱欣 不問自取及拖欠退款（犯刑事及無申報兼職） <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1146084/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1146084/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n多謝各路英雄鼎力支持，希望更加多人知道哩件事，避免有下一位受害者。<br />\n<br />\n2019年5月12日更新<br />\n根據施小聰身邊人爆料 施小聰今年轉左荃灣商會學校任教<br />\n施小聰已經比今年任教學校割蓆要求離職<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJNjbKw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJNjbKw.png&h=f935c8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聲稱換電話及新FACEBOOK<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1xqwNiC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1xqwNiC.png&h=415af9e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另有施小聰身邊人爆料 施小聰屋企人均任職工程大判<br />\n手上持有屯門市廣場、康麗花園、帝濤灣多個單位<br />\n絕對有能力還款及懷疑施小聰扮窮騙取公屋及香港房屋協會獎助學金等學費資助<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>懶人包</strong></span><br />\n主角：施小聰（事主）池凱欣（老婆)<br />\n中學就讀學校：嗇色園主辦可藝中學<br />\n中學後就讀：嶺南大學社區學院 - 電腦學高級文憑課程<br />\n其後疑似就讀：HKU Postgrad dip 教育文憑<br />\n<br />\n18年度前任教學校：浸信會永隆中學<br />\n18-19年度任教學校：荃灣商會學校(已在5月12日被學校要求離職)<br />\n現任教學校或工作：？<br />\n住址：天x圍 天晴邨 <br />\n電話號碼：+852 6179 9996<br />\n車牌號碼：UX3994<br />\nFacebook: Rex Sy<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rex.sy.54\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frex.sy.54&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa5Aoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=cd18fe69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rex.sy.54</a><br />\n施小聰做admin既搵食Facebook群組 已開辦多團改車團購: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/477249456089824/members/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F477249456089824%2Fmembers%2F&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa5Aoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=7f46a472\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/477249456089824/members/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WinUScp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWinUScp.jpg&h=cd09daf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQGuF5K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQGuF5K.png&h=224a48a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原受害人樓主：<br />\n施小聰係Facebook Prius車group到話自己買賣汽車包圍，所以今年1月初，就聯絡左施小聰買頭尾包圍裙腳。佢好有效率咁幫我訂好同安裝個頭尾包圍和裙腳。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AN3tccG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAN3tccG.png&h=e2d43b39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年1月11日<br />\n原樓主去相熟車房整車，發覺一月初暫放喺車房嘅汽車零件消失。及後得悉，原來係施小聰拎咗，當時車房佬有提醒施小聰要得原樓主批准先可以拎走，但係施小聰並冇理會，並將原樓主套原裝包圍安裝落自己架車到。到原樓主知道咗，施小聰就話會拆翻俾原樓主。<br />\n<br />\n同日，原樓主夜晚再入數俾施小聰幫訂套新裙腳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Ln059.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Ln059.png&h=45efe054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年2月至4月<br />\n經多翻追問，施小聰都係用拖或者唔覆嘅方式話遲下會拆翻套原裝包圍俾原樓主。哩段時間內，都有問究竟另外入數訂果套裙腳幾時有，係咁推遲推遲，足足等咗差唔多3個半至4個月。<br />\n施小聰擅自用咗原樓主套原裝包圍幾個月，原樓主就提岀叫施小聰俾$3000當買斷套原裝包圍，因為套包圍比佢拿左去用左差唔多半年都已經唔係全新，施小聰話會度度佢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sYxabE1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsYxabE1.png&h=8b5e68d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VDMm2NN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDMm2NN.png&h=f913f0be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年5月5日<br />\n已經覺得等得太耐好過份，所以俾最後一次機會施小聰，希望佢7日內可以俾到追加訂單的裙腳同$3000買斷佢偷左果套原裝包圍解決件事，否則報警處理。施小聰竟然態度依舊，並支持報警處理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNu7Ymk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNu7Ymk.png&h=a30e2b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NeUS9s4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNeUS9s4.png&h=a816eaa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>另一受害人K先生</strong><br />\n2018年12月<br />\nK先生聯絡施小聰買全車包圍加尾翼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ncky7Ps.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fncky7Ps.png&h=da513acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年1月<br />\n施小聰話同某間車房發生事，所以啲貨比人扣起咗，要再訂過哂所有野。之後就一直話未搞點，又話噴油初10先開工，K先生一直催施小聰幾時先有貨。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LR5LeuA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLR5LeuA.png&h=12ac19c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3MF3LBf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3MF3LBf.png&h=098576e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ukshP2W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FukshP2W.png&h=f026b4a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QC6eSgg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQC6eSgg.png&h=f8f8ba52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVx9F9B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVx9F9B.png&h=cde5c8ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年3月<br />\nK先生認為等得太耐，要求退還欠款$6000港幣。施小聰回應如果月尾無貨就會退款。到三月尾依然無貨，K先生不斷問幾時退款，施小聰就已讀不回。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ww8wUtK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fww8wUtK.png&h=23bfd97b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v1EPF8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv1EPF8L.png&h=4860afd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PvQLetL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPvQLetL.png&h=8a06c306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sLVZ3m5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsLVZ3m5.png&h=33887a95&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QOfOWG6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQOfOWG6.png&h=289c5f77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年5月5日<br />\nK先生俾最後一次機會施小聰退款，否則報警處理，而施小聰就話報啦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVzHgHg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVzHgHg.png&h=39eb447f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC9DztW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC9DztW.png&h=dfb32de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zg8domF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZg8domF.png&h=3e8526e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n施小聰挑釁原樓主即管把事主貼上LIHKG 佢唔會驚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m5UNkLH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm5UNkLH.png&h=c26dd4b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原樓主連登開po後，施小聰身邊人爆料施小聰當年欺凌同學影片及今年連google都搜尋唔到既任教學校，就收到施小聰老婆池凱欣嘅電話，希望和解，但係態度依舊，並說出將偷左既原裝包圍拆返落黎歸還大家當完左件事的荒謬說話。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o5Dpgbn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo5Dpgbn.png&h=a1b403fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eOVCBbn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeOVCBbn.png&h=0bf75528&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FieS9wn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFieS9wn.png&h=8cd6c56d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原樓主聽到拆返套偷左既包圍整返靚仔當無件事嬲到無計傾後，多名苦主均收到133來電滋擾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YU047rx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYU047rx.png&h=128efad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時，有巴打爆料原來施小聰10年前喺學校欺凌同學，更疑似害死受害人。有片為證，施小聰係白色衫者。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p1X2gJ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp1X2gJ3.jpg&h=5c8a2f16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vakmXOzC3Bw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvakmXOzC3Bw&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa5Aoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=dcad266c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vakmXOzC3Bw</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0upVH-HODDc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0upVH-HODDc&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa5Aoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=2a9d44f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0upVH-HODDc</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6EfZPxf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6EfZPxf.png&h=6200938d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yn7tHSf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyn7tHSf.png&h=66734b0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20060924/6341805\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20060924%2F6341805&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa5Aoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=7c75d2ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20060924%2F6341805&h=86fd6767\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledail